## **1. Background & Rise of the Gupta Empire**

**Predecessors (Before Guptas):**

* **Kushanas** (North-West India) â€“ declined around 3rd century CE.
* **Satavahanas** (Deccan) â€“ weakened after 200 CE.
* India politically fragmented after their fall.
* **Magadha region** regained prominence under Guptas.
* **Chandragupta I** gained power through **marriage alliance with the Lichchhavi princess Kumaradevi**.

**Foundation:**

* Around **320 CE**, Chandragupta I established the Gupta dynasty.
* Marked the beginning of the **Gupta Era (320 CE)**.

